A '''Dark Side Daiquiri''' was a [[Alcohol/Legends|mixed drink]] served at [[Republic Mobile Surgical Unit 7]]'s [[Cantina/Legends|cantina]] during the [[Battle of Drongar]]. The [[Falleen/Legends|Falleen]] criminal [[Thula]] had consumed this beverage when she reported her success in tricking the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Republic]] [[Quartermaster/Legends|quartermaster]] [[Nars Dojah]] into hiring her to [[Kaird]].

